---
title: Pronto Italian Style Sausage Meatballs with Pesto Tomato Sauce and Mash
description: Hey presto! These speedy Pronto Italian Style Sausage Meatballs are ready in under 25 minutes. Using herby oregano sausage meat makes the meatballs come together quickly to save time but still make a dinner that's full of flavour.
